# ============================================
# Google Maps API Configuration
# ============================================
# IMPORTANT: You MUST obtain your own Google Maps API key
# This is a security requirement - do not use placeholder values in production
# 
# Steps to get your API key:
# 1. Go to: https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Create a new project or select existing project
# 3. Enable "Maps JavaScript API" and "Places API"
# 4. Go to "Credentials" → "Create Credentials" → "API Key"
# 5. Copy the API key and paste it below
# 6. (Optional) Restrict the API key to your domain for security
# ============================================
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=YOUR_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY_HERE

